@LivenessAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5038

### Start a session (replace with a real base64 JPEG/PNG of a face)
POST {{LivenessAPI_HostAddress}}/api/liveness/session/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "referenceImageBase64": "<base64-reference-photo>"
}

### Submit a frame (use the sessionId returned above)
POST {{LivenessAPI_HostAddress}}/api/liveness/session/{{sessionId}}/frame
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageBase64": "<base64-camera-frame>"
}

### Check session status
GET {{LivenessAPI_HostAddress}}/api/liveness/session/{{sessionId}}/status
Accept: application/json

###
